<p><strong>Sources</strong> <Link to="/source/paizo_blog___golarion_day_subdomains">Paizo Blog - Golarion Day Subdomains</Link><br/>These adjustments make the Death domain more in line with <Link to="/faith/pharasma">Pharasma's</Link> tenets.</p>
